        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" VerticalAlignment="Top" FontSize="11"><Hyperlink Click="Hyperlink_Click" NavigateUri="https://github.com/JDrocks450/nio2so">nio2so</Hyperlink> <Run> was created by Jeremy Glazebrook (bisquick)</Run></TextBlock>
        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" VerticalAlignment="Top" FontSize="11"><Run>Special thanks to </Run> <Hyperlink Click="Hyperlink_Click" NavigateUri="https://github.com/daddesio/Niotso">niotso</Hyperlink> (FatBag/daddesio)</TextBlock>
        <Button Margin="5" Click="Button_Click">Thank you!</Button>
    </StackPanel>
</Window>
